model.name: AI Leadership Pulse
model.description: A quick assessment of how you work with AI today and what you know about how it functions.

maturityScale.name: Fundamental
maturityScale.description: Starter with AI skills; develop prompting skills

maturityScale.name: Intermediate
maturityScale.description: Baseline skills suggest readiness for more advanced automation and agent use.

maturityScale.name: Agent Boss
maturityScale.description: Your core AI skills and knowledge suggest exploring customer personal agents in more depth.

dimensions.label: Skills
dimensions.description: Your personal capability for interacting with AI systems

dimensions.label: Knowledge
dimensions.description: Your understanding of how AI processes operate

questions.text: Which best describes how you’ve set up AI “instructions” or custom settings (ChatGPT or Copilot)?

answers.text: Never
I know about it but can't find them
I have a basic set of instructions
I have different sets of instructions for chat, notebooks and agents.

questions.text: When you ask AI to draft or analyze, what’s your typical approach?

answers.text: Single prompt; accept first result
Add some context; light edits
Structured prompt + 1–2 iterations
Multi-step prompt workflow + prompt library

questions.text: Your experience creating or using task-specific agents (e.g., interview agent, research assistant, custom GPT):

answers.text: None
Tried a prebuilt template (Researcher, Sora) once
I use Researcher and other agents regularly.
Built/maintain custom agents used by my team.

questions.text: How do generative AI tools (like Copilot or ChatGPT) produce answers to your prompts?

answers.text: They predict words based on patterns learned from large datasets, not by recalling exact facts
They do a real-time internet search and return verbatim information
They pull answers from a static database of Q&A
A human operator writes the responses live
I don't know
Software that seacrhes the internet and answers questions, summarizes, or builds new content.
Software that executes automatoc workflow on documents
Software that's able to execute ambiguous tasks with autonomy
Software that schedule AI prompts on an ongoing schedule
I don't know

questions.text: You’re drafting a customer message and want to improve it using AI. What’s the best prompt?

answers.text: Make this better.
Rewrite this message so it’s shorter.
Improve clarity, keep the tone professional and empathetic, and highlight next steps clearly.
Rewrite this for the customer.
I don't know.
